  <name>IPlan</name>
  <summary>Your plan for improving personal life and workflow</summary>
  <description>
    <p>IPlan goal is to be a user friendly tool for those who want to organize their personal life or jobs.</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Grouping tasks with project and list</li>
      <li>Timer for tasks</li>
      <li>Subtasks</li>
      <li>Global search</li>
      <li>Arranging projects, lists, and tasks by drag and drop</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
